commentary: Williamson to Sikandar Raza, OUT what's happened there?! Outstanding fielding from Martin Guptill. Raza had gone on the back foot to push a ball towards mid-on, and Williams set off for a run from the non-striker's end. Guptill came sprinting in from midwicket to dive full length and cut off the shot. Seeing that, Raza sent Williams back ... Guptill was still flat on the ground on his stomach when he back-handed the ball along the ground and hit the stumps direct to run Williams out by miles
